title: How This Woman Scammed JP Morgan
description:
In this episode, we take a look at the story of Charlie Javis. A young entrepreneur who lied her way into a deal with JP Morgan. The bank quickly found out about the fraud and she could now be facing 100 years in jail.

Intro: Burn Water - Getting Older
Outro: Burn Water - Adomania
